 Ensuring sustainable climate and disaster risk financing is available to countries that face extreme weather events in Africa, sits at the heart of the African Risk Capacity’s mandate. Join CNBC Africa from the side-lines of the African Development Bank’s annual meetings in Busan, South Korea, as we hear stories from countries that have benefited from the Africa Disaster Risk Financing Programme.
